display_long_description:
Step into the absurd universe of Doctor Galaxy, where mad science collides with intergalactic nonsense in this hilarious VR sandbox. As the eccentric doctor, your mission is to create bizarre alien specimens and send them on unpredictable journeys across the galaxy.

Mix and match body parts, paint them, and use futuristic tools to unleash endless combinations. Every experiment becomes a brand-new adventure filled with chaotic humor and surprising results.

Key Features:

 🧬 Body Modification: Swap, remove, and fuse alien parts to design the most ridiculous specimens imaginable. Each strange combination unlocks fresh ways to play.
[media]

 ⚙️ 3D Printing Lab: Print ready-to-use alien limbs, tentacles, mechanical arms, and iconic variations with endless replayability.
[media]

 🎨 Painting Customization: Spray, color, and cover your creations with impossible shades and colors that bring them to life in VR.
[media]

 🌌 Galactic Delivery: Once complete, launch your specimens to distant planets and watch your twisted creations go to different worlds.
[media]

Can you build the weirdest lifeforms in the galaxy? Enter Doctor Galaxy today and let your imagination run wild in a VR experience where every failed experiment is just another reason to laugh.
